Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
I think that this is a very good thing because it forces young students to interact with others in their dorm.  This is good teaching for later in life.  It teaches students to compromise, work together, solve problems, and by extension, causes them to mature.